ome.smuggler.core.service.file.impl

Class TSafeKeyValueStore<K extends util.object.Identifiable,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ome.smuggler.core.service.file.impl.TSafeKeyValueStore<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeyValueStore<K,V>

    public class TSafeKeyValueStore<K extends util.object.Identifiable,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements KeyValueStore<K,V>
    Wraps a KeyValueStore to make it thread safe. This class uses lock striping to serialise operations on the same key while at the same time allowing operations on different keys to run in parallel.
